<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="~/css/landing.css" />

@{
    Layout = "_Layout";
}

<!-- Hero Section -->
<div class="jumbotron text-center">
    <h1 class="display-4">Learn More About Bumblebee Foundation</h1>
    <p>Explore more about our foundation and the impact we are creating.</p>
</div>

<!-- Information Cards Section -->
<div class="container my-5">
    <div class="row">
        <!-- Card 1: Donor -->
        <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
            <div class="card" style="background-color: var(--color-pastel-green); border: none; height: 100%; border-radius: 10px;">
                <div class="card-body" style="color: var(--text);">
                    <h5 class="card-title" style="color: var(--text); font-size: 1.5rem;">Donor</h5>
                    <div class="card-text" style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
                        <p>Becoming a Donor: What You Can Do</p>
                        <p>
                            As a donor, your journey begins by entering all the necessary details in the required fields to register an account. This step ensures we have accurate information to provide you with the best experience. If you already have an account, simply log in to access your dashboard.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Once logged in, you can explore various features designed to enhance your giving experience. Your dashboard provides an overview of ongoing projects, allowing you to view detailed information about each initiative. You can browse through all available projects you can contribute to, learn about their goals, and choose the ones that align with your interests.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Additionally, your dashboard keeps a record of your donation history, giving you a clear picture of your contributions over time. This feature helps you track the impact of your generosity and manage your charitable activities effortlessly.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 2: Company -->
        <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
            <div class="card" style="background-color: var(--color-pastel-green); border: none; height: 100%; border-radius: 10px;">
                <div class="card-body" style="color: var(--text);">
                    <h5 class="card-title" style="color: var(--text); font-size: 1.5rem;">Company</h5>
                    <div class="card-text" style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
                        <p>For Companies: What You Can Do</p>
                        <p>
                            As a company, the first step is to register an account by entering all the required details in the designated fields. This ensures your organization's information is properly recorded. If you already have an account, simply log in to access your dashboard.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Once logged in, you have the ability to update your organization’s details as needed. Keeping your information up-to-date ensures smooth communication and better collaboration on projects.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Additionally, you can create projects and submit them for approval. These projects, once approved, will be made available for donors to view and contribute to, enabling your organization to achieve its goals effectively.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="jumbotron text-center" style="background-color: #E0EDC5; padding: 40px;">
    <h3 class="display-3" style="color: #000000;">Frequently Asked Questions</h3>
    <p style="color: #333;">Find answers to the most common questions about the Bumblebee Foundation website.</p>

    <div class="accordion" id="faqAccordion" style="max-width: 600px; margin: auto; text-align: left; background-color: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
        <!-- Question 1 -->
        <div class="accordion-item" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
                <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseOne" style="background-color: #ffffff; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;">
                    How do I make a donation?
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body" style="background-color: #ffffff; color: #000000;">
                    In order to make a donation, you will first need to find a project you would like to contribute to. Once on the project details page, you will have the option to make a donation through our Paystack services.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Question 2 -->
        <div class="accordion-item" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo" style="background-color: #ffffff; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;">
                    How do I cancel my recurring payment?
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body" style="background-color: #ffffff; color: #000000;">
                    In order to cancel a recurring payment, your email invoice offers an option to directly cancel your scheduled payment.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Question 3 -->
        <div class="accordion-item" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree" style="background-color: #ffffff; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;">
                    Where can I find my donation invoice?
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body" style="background-color: #ffffff; color: #000000;">
                    For every donation made, whether once-off or recurring, your invoice will be emailed directly to the associated email address of the donation.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

       
    </div>
</div>


